raw_text: PHYLLIS MINSHULL (nee APONSO),​ at rest with Jesus. Beloved wife of the late Douglas,​ daughter of the late ELW Aponso and Sally Aponso,​ sister of the late Leslie Aponso,​ Sylvia de Mel,​ Enid Ranasinghe and Quintus Aponso. Viewing at A.F. Raymonds Funeral Parlour from 10.00 a.m. on Monday 24.07.2023. Cortege leaves the parlour at 3.30 p.m. for a service at the Holy Emmanuel Church,​ Moratuwa at 4.30 p.m. followed by the burial in the Church Cemetery.045656
